## Proposed changes


This commit contains some improvements:
1. Improve the scaling out speed, especially for small tablets. It's rather quickly to copy small tablets.  So we set the balance sched period from 1s to 100ms;
2. Make repairing task prior to balance task. When wanting to add balance tasks to the pending queue, we first check if there are enough slots.  So if there are running repairing task and they have taking all the slots. Then no balance task could add to pending queue until there's available slots;
3. When adding a new replica, select the be with min load;
4. Hdd and ssd use different  slot nums;
5. Put the running failed sched ctx back to pending queue cause the scheduler will not re-sched ctxs in the running queue;
6. TabletSchedCtx brief info add tablet size.


